{"tid":2447405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柴灣環翠邨足球場淪「燒烤場」　10多人圍爐BBQ遺一地垃圾","createTime":"2021-03-15T07:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T08:35:11.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4121b1aaca524a393fdb3a087a64b7233dfca2c9","tid":2447405,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901261/bbq_thumb_20210315_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901261%2Fbbq_thumb_20210315_S_600.jpg&h=39a60cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 柴灣環翠邨足球場淪「燒烤場」，10多人圍爐BBQ遺一地垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n疫情持續，郊野公園的燒烤場仍然關閉，但近日卻有人在柴灣環翠邨的足球場搭爐燒烤，其後保安到場驅趕，他們才收爐離開。區議員吳卓燁表示，近期已屢次發生同類事件，事後遺下大量垃圾，嚴重影響衛生。<br />\n<br />\n區議員吳卓燁日前於Facebook發文表示，接獲街坊投訴，有人於環翠邨足球場內燒烤，他聯同保安員趕到現場，發現有10多人正在燒烤，保安員即時警告他們立即離開，否則報警處理，他們聞言隨即「收爐走人」。從圖片可見，他們在地上放置燒烤爐具，並自備炭和食物，而遍地都是膠袋、紙杯紙碟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901261/158602977_503481454371921_2303374992656526053_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901261%2F158602977_503481454371921_2303374992656526053_o_600.jpg&h=fe65f53d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901261/139921812_470657614320972_1131027303165365248_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901261%2F139921812_470657614320972_1131027303165365248_n_600.jpg&h=41426409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901261/140235811_470657577654309_292014179931340540_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901261%2F140235811_470657577654309_292014179931340540_n_600.jpg&h=813eebb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901261/139023199_467142914672442_3472081027402998096_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901261%2F139023199_467142914672442_3472081027402998096_o_600.jpg&h=63d5aa02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901261/139748985_467142784672455_5025744127006044016_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901261%2F139748985_467142784672455_5025744127006044016_n_600.jpg&h=0e91c0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳卓燁表示，過往亦多次發現有人於足球場內燒烤，形容這次終於「人贓並獲」。據他早前的Facebook貼文可見，1月時已有多名街坊投訴，指在家中聞到燒烤氣味，並持續逾1小時，亦有住高層的居民看到有火光。<br />\n當時他與保安到現場了解，「發現人就走晒，嗰爐仲燒緊雞翼」，更留下一地垃圾，造成衛生問題。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;食到咁上下就拍拍屁股走人，依家夜麻麻 無清潔姐姐可以幫手，焗住要擺過夜。垃圾搞到成個足球場都係，大佬啊，係咪想養米奇、養強哥？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民關注，不少人批評燒烤人士缺乏公德心，並違反限聚令，構成傳播風險，「真係以為邊度燒都得」、「應該報警啦，又唔只一次系度燒烤」、「不應放生」。"},{"pid":"c74c105360fc7ef9e9a941a0558913835114ee74","tid":2447405,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"呢個足球場使用率好低？<br />\n夜晚周圍都爆滿架喎"},{"pid":"ffc86ce97b2a8355f12bb388616c1e51cc93f7ad","tid":2447405,"uid":264199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"柴灣唔係仲有單係屋邨後山政府地種菜？ 有埋水池？<br />\n橫頭橫尾特別多呢D野"},{"pid":"06c8a01ddb219ab28e71e4656b030759687adcea","tid":2447405,"uid":257184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"呢單同屋苑燒煙花嗰單，已完全體現中國同香港嘅完美溶合，恭喜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}